  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 1</strong> Divination</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> sphere</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Concentration, up to 10 minutes</p>\n\nFor the duration, you sense the presence of magical effects within 30 feet of yourself. If you sense such effects, you can take the Magic|XPHB action to see a faint aura around any visible creature or object in the area that bears the magic, and if an effect was created by a spell, you learn the spell's school of magic|XPHB|7|Schools of Magic. The spell is blocked by 1 foot of stone, dirt, or wood; 1 inch of metal; or a thin sheet of lead.",
